            .vert-align
                .container
                    .container.white-text.center
                        h1.header.center.text-lighten-2.hide-on-med-and-down Matěj "Horm" Horák
                        h2.header.center.text-lighten-2.hide-on-med-and-up Matěj Horák
                        .row.center
                            p.flow-text
                                | I&apos;m software developer, GDG organizer or just a man who likes technologies. You may know my nickname
                                | Horm but I&apos;m not sure if you know something about me. So let&apos;s start scrolling or click on some links
                                | below to see some new about me!
                        .row.center
                            .divider
                        .row.center
                            .col.s2
                                a(href='https://twitter.com/horakmat', target='_blank').white-text
