                                    i.fab.fa-stack-overflow.fa-3x
                            |
                            .col.s2
                                a(href='https://linkedin.com/in/horakmat', target='_blank').white-text
                                    i.fab.fa-linkedin.fa-3x
                            |
                            .col.s2
                                a(href='https://github.com/Horm', target='_blank').white-text
                                    i.fab.fa-github.fa-3x
                            |
                            .col.s2
                                a(href='https://medium.com/@horm', target='_blank').white-text
                                    i.fab.fa-medium.fa-3x
                            |
                            .col.s2
                                a(href='https://instagram.com/horakmat', target='_blank').white-text
                                    i.fab.fa-instagram.fa-3x

                        br

        .container
            .section
                // Icon Section
                h2 Who am I?
                p.lead
                    | When you say name Matěj Horák, you can expect person, who has many activities and
                    | interests.
                    | Hard to say what is my aim in life but I just want to help somehow and be happy.
                    | How? Apart from writing the code, organizing events with GDG and
                    | playing the guitar, I try to live every day as good as possible.

                .row
                    .col.s12.m2
                        br
                        br
                        img.circle.responsive-img(src='images/profilepic.jpg', alt='')
                    .col.s12.m1
                    .col.s12.m9

                        h3 Developer
                        p
                        | Since my childhood I've found computers very interesting and thanks to programming I can create many new
                        | things as websites, mobile applications or smart hidden tools.
                        p
                        | When I learned some new programming technologies I've found communities very helpful. I feel the duty to
                        | reciprocate it so I'm organizer in Google Developer Group in Czech Republic.
                        |
                        h3 Musician
                        p
                        | I play the electric guitar. It&apos;s my favourite hobby because during the playing I can clear my head. I&apos;m
                        | playing in the small band. I don&apos;t have favourites genres but my favourite bands are Simple Plan,
                        | Paramore and Coldplay.
                        h3 Sport Lover
                        p
                        | Not like a professional but sport is one important part of my free time. Minimally once a week I play floorbal and go jogging.
                        | For transport in a city usually I go by skateboard.

                br
                br
                br


        .bg-skills
            .section
                .container

                    h2.header.white-text Skills
                    p.light.white-text I have some experience with many technologies, frameworks, parts of development but these are my favourites. In any case, I prefer Test Driven Development and clean code practices like functional concepts.

                    .row
                        mixin skill(name, icon, text)
                            .col.s12.m4
                                .icon-block
                                    h2.center.white-text
                                        i(class=icon)
                                    h3.center.orange-text !{name}
                                    p.light.white-text.center !{text}
                        +skill("Kotlin", "fab fa-kickstarter-k", "I can develop in Java but I think there is no reason for that. Kotlin is good in using different paradigms such as functional or object oriented programming etc.")
                        +skill("JavaScript", "fab fa-js", "Freedom but responsibility, that's the rule. It's not about types. I like Javascript because it's not necessary to write so many keywords to simple object or function...")
                        +skill("Git", "fas fa-code-branch", "Is there someone who is using some other VCS tool? I'm big open source fan. You can check my GitHub to see some my open source contributions...")
                    .row
                        +skill("Frontend", "fas fa-desktop", "I have experience with developing native Android and iOS applications. What about web? For now, only AngularJS yet. However, my bachelor work will be in React.")
                        +skill("Backend", "fas fa-database", "ExpressJS, Spring or Firebase but I do not prefer Firebase as backend solution.")
                        +skill("TDD", "fas fa-check", "If I can, I'm writing tests. It's not possible to have 100% code coverage but tests help you with safe refactoring, adding new features and testing your implementations.")
                    br
        .container
            .section
                h2 Active in Community
                p Since I have started to study programming I wanted to visit some space where is possible share our knowledge and learn from each other. Luckily I have found GDG community in Czechia and after one month I joined this community, concretely I have created local chapter in Žďár nad Sázavou.
                p Now, I am active in GDG Brno. We organized many types of events like talks, workshops, coding dojos or conference DevFest. I was mentoring Angular Workshop and in 2017 I attended Google I/O in Mountain View.
                br
                .slider
                    ul.slides
                        li
                            img(src='images/community/org-dark.jpg')
                            // random image
                            .caption.left-align
                                h3 Organizer of GDG Brno
                                h5.light.grey-text.text-lighten-3 Talks, Workshops, Coding Dojos...
                        li
                            img(src='images/community/io-dark.jpg')
                            // random image
                            .caption.left-align
                                br
                                br
                                br
                                br
                                br
                                br
                                br
                                h3 Google I/O
                                h5.light.grey-text.text-lighten-3 Me in Silicon Valley...
                        li
                            img(src='images/community/a2-mentor-dark.jpg')
                            // random image
                            .caption.right-align
                                br
                                br
                                br
                                br
                                br
                                br
                                h3 Angular Workshop Mentor
                                h5.light.grey-text.text-lighten-3 I helped with Angular workshop...

                        li
                            img(src='images/community/devfest-dark.jpg')
                            // random image
                            .caption.center-align
                                br
                                br
                                br
                                br
                                br
                                br
                                br
                                br
                                h3 DevFest Conference
                                h5.light.grey-text.text-lighten-3 I helped with DevFest in Pilsen and twice in Prague...
                br

        .bg-projects
            .section.no-pad-bot
                .container
                    h2.white-text Portfolio highlights
                    .row
                        mixin project(html, cover, title, note)
                            .col.s12.m6
                                a(href=html)
                                    .card.hoverable
                                        .card-image
                                            img(src=cover)
                                        .card-content
                                            span.card-title.black-text=title
                                            p.black-text=note
                        +project("gugweb.html", "images/portfolio/modals/m-gug.jpg", "GUG.cz Web", "Web for publishing Google User Group events")
                        +project("raytools.html", "images/portfolio/modals/m-raytools.jpg", "RAy Tools", "Android and iOS native applications for easy microwave link setup")
                br

        .section
            .container
                div.center
                    h2 Contact Me
                    p If you want to ask me about my person, projects or some technology please use this email:
                    br
                    a.center(href="mailto:info@horm.cz")
                        i.fas.fa-5x.fa-envelope.orange-text
                        p.flow-text.lead.orange-text info@horm.cz
                    p In case of job offers...
                    br
                    a.btn-large.orange(href="mailto:info@horm.cz?subject=Job Offer: Company Name") Send Job Offer
                    br
                    br
                    br

        footer.page-footer.grey.darken-3
